the bad experiences

01:19:05.950 --> 01:19:09.037
are as important
as the good ones,

01:19:09.162 --> 01:19:11.455
I mean,
I was in Jerry's life

01:19:11.664 --> 01:19:14.458
because, apparently,
he needed to work through

01:19:14.458 --> 01:19:16.460
some dreary episode
with his mother,

01:19:16.502 --> 01:19:18.462
