ruins more lives

01:19:29.347 --> 01:19:32.933
than all the diseases
known to man,

01:19:33.059 --> 01:19:35.185
Get back in the saddle
again, honey,

01:19:35.311 --> 01:19:37.980
No way, I can't
let this happen again,

01:19:37.980 --> 01:19:41.191
