01:23:00.749 --> 01:23:02.584
You know,
it's hard to believe

01:23:02.709 --> 01:23:03.543
you're Melanie's
grandmother,

01:23:03.668 --> 01:23:05.628
When did you
get married, 12?

01:23:10.341 --> 01:23:12.343
I love L, A,

01:23:12.468 --> 01:23:14.887
