01:23:40.535 --> 01:23:42.287
That was great,

01:23:42.496 --> 01:23:45.081
So here it is,
my dressing room,

01:23:45.081 --> 01:23:47.917
[Whispering] Melanie,
Oh, my God,

01:23:48.001 --> 01:23:50.670
Oh, honey, Oh, Mel,

01:23:50.711 --> 01:23:52.129
