of triumph

01:24:00.429 --> 01:24:02.931
and of joy
in this family?

01:24:04.599 --> 01:24:07.018
Oh, Mel,
How far you've come,

01:24:07.101 --> 01:24:08.311
How much
you've accomplished,

01:24:08.353 --> 01:24:11.731
Just think,
less than a year ago,

01:24:11.731 --> 01:24:14.567
you were lying in a hospital
near death,

01:24:14.692 --> 01:24:16.735
