and I don't back-stab,

01:26:39.658 --> 01:26:41.118
This is about Jerry,
isn't it?

01:26:41.201 --> 01:26:42.202
This is about
Melanie!

01:26:42.285 --> 01:26:44.454
Oh, please, Aurora,
That again?

01:26:44.537 --> 01:26:46.581
